          "name": "Howl of the Wild",
          "page": 178,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Leopard seals are a large species of seals, often growing up to ten feet long. They're the only species of seal known to pursue humanoids.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
